$ VBA - language: converting a date into a string

The → development/languages/VBA/functions/format[`format`] function allows to convert a → development/languages/VBA/language/datatypes/date[date] into a
→ development/languages/VBA/language/datatypes/string[string].

Note: minutes are represented by an unintuitive `n`.

